01:17:20.236 --> 01:17:21.705
What are those?
That's trouble.

01:17:21.705 --> 01:17:23.773
I want you to call
911 right now.

01:17:23.807 --> 01:17:25.174
Right now, child!
Go!

01:17:25.208 --> 01:17:26.976
All right. I will.

01:17:27.010 --> 01:17:28.912
Come on, baby.

01:17:28.945 --> 01:17:30.213
[Groans]

01:17:30.246 --> 01:17:31.715
[Gagging]

01:17:37.186 --> 01:17:39.022
Butch!

01:17:39.055 --> 01:17:41.357
Butch! Butch!

01:17:41.390 --> 01:17:43.092
