You need
to help her!

01:18:21.464 --> 01:18:23.833
I can't get my hand
in there!
What do you mean?

01:18:23.867 --> 01:18:25.835
Why is she
doing this?!
What happened?!

01:18:25.869 --> 01:18:26.870
