01:19:42.111 --> 01:19:44.280
[Moans]

01:20:44.340 --> 01:20:46.442
You almost died today.

01:20:47.977 --> 01:20:50.947
Told you I'd find
a way to screw it up.

01:20:53.282 --> 01:20:55.118
So what's with
the Vicodin?

01:20:59.222 --> 01:21:01.357
Old habits die hard.

01:21:03.026 --> 01:21:04.961
You hitched your trailer
to a loser.

01:21:04.994 --> 01:21:06.062
