what's going on
in my life right now.

01:21:24.147 --> 01:21:25.982
Look at me.
There's a little girl
in there

01:21:26.015 --> 01:21:27.583
that loves you
more than anything
in the world,

01:21:27.616 --> 01:21:29.452
and you're all
the family she has.

01:21:29.485 --> 01:21:32.088
