the only thing
holding us together.

01:21:47.436 --> 01:21:49.505
I never failed
anything in my life,

01:21:49.538 --> 01:21:54.310
but I blame myself
for not being able
to take care of her,

01:21:54.343 --> 01:21:56.012
and I
promised myself

01:21:56.045 --> 01:21:58.281
I wouldn't get close
to anyone again,

01:21:58.314 --> 01:22:01.384
I wouldn't fail
somebody again.

01:22:01.417 --> 01:22:03.586
But along you come.

01:22:05.288 --> 01:22:08.491
For the first time
in a long time,

01:22:08.524 --> 01:22:10.994
