with saying it?

01:22:23.106 --> 01:22:24.573
Because I love you, too,

01:22:24.607 --> 01:22:27.210
and I... I know that
when I want something,

01:22:27.243 --> 01:22:30.079
it's like we both said
before, we mess it up.

01:22:30.113 --> 01:22:31.480
But we can
do it together.

01:22:31.514 --> 01:22:33.516
I want a family.
I want you,

01:22:33.549 --> 01:22:35.518
and I want that...
I do, too.

01:22:37.186 --> 01:22:39.122
But how will
we make it work?

01:22:39.155 --> 01:22:41.290
'Cause every time
I look at you,

01:22:41.324 --> 01:22:44.260
you take
my breath away,

01:22:44.293 --> 01:22:46.229
and when
I'm not with you...

01:22:47.696 --> 01:22:50.033
my heart aches.

01:22:51.334 --> 01:22:53.602
So you think that
I'm gonna leave that

01:22:53.636 --> 01:22:56.205
after I've looked
for it my whole life,

01:22:56.239 --> 01:22:58.041
