01:26:07.496 --> 01:26:09.565
It's tough.
It's just the way it is.

01:26:09.598 --> 01:26:11.534
Good.

01:26:13.236 --> 01:26:14.237
[Sighs]

01:26:14.237 --> 01:26:15.338
I should
go over there.

01:26:15.371 --> 01:26:16.472
All right.

01:26:16.505 --> 01:26:17.973
