of a lot of people.

01:27:48.931 --> 01:27:50.933
You know that?

01:27:50.966 --> 01:27:52.034
Really?

01:27:52.067 --> 01:27:53.035
Oh, yeah.

01:27:53.068 --> 01:27:55.604
