you're less of a sister.

01:28:45.954 --> 01:28:47.623
You either.

01:28:49.692 --> 01:28:51.394
Not in my eyes.

01:28:51.427 --> 01:28:53.862
[Wind blowing]

01:28:53.896 --> 01:28:55.998
