[Joe Boy squeals]

01:30:18.481 --> 01:30:19.448
It's okay.

01:30:19.482 --> 01:30:20.916
Easy, boy.

01:30:20.949 --> 01:30:22.050
Easy.

01:30:23.752 --> 01:30:25.954
That-a-boy.

01:30:25.988 --> 01:30:27.590
That-a-boy.

01:30:28.657 --> 01:30:29.792
[Neighs]
Easy.

01:30:29.825 --> 01:30:31.927
Whoa.
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

01:30:31.960 --> 01:30:34.062
Whoa. Hey.

01:30:34.096 --> 01:30:36.765
All right,
that's it.

01:30:36.799 --> 01:30:38.000
