What's wrong?

01:30:43.939 --> 01:30:44.907
What's wrong, buddy?

01:30:44.940 --> 01:30:47.042
What's wrong?

01:30:47.075 --> 01:30:48.911
[Thunder crashes]
Uhh!

01:30:54.617 --> 01:30:56.519
[Neighs]

