It's Butch!
What?

01:31:32.921 --> 01:31:33.889
It's Butch.

01:31:33.922 --> 01:31:35.558
Oh, my God.

01:31:35.558 --> 01:31:37.593
Oh, my God. Butch.

01:31:37.626 --> 01:31:39.227
Butch!
Butch!

01:31:40.295 --> 01:31:41.630
Butch!
Butch!

01:31:41.664 --> 01:31:42.631
Oh, my God!

