01:31:57.212 --> 01:31:58.647
Come on, Butch!

01:31:58.681 --> 01:31:59.648
Come on!
Stay with me!

01:31:59.682 --> 01:32:00.649
Wake up!
Come on! Come on!

01:32:00.683 --> 01:32:01.650
Come on!

01:32:01.684 --> 01:32:04.086
Stay with me,
