01:32:04.119 --> 01:32:05.588
[Siren blaring]

01:32:05.588 --> 01:32:07.122
Blood pressure falling!

01:32:13.862 --> 01:32:15.931
White male, 42,
found unconscious.

01:32:15.964 --> 01:32:17.633
Blunt force trauma
to the head.

01:32:17.666 --> 01:32:20.603
Prep him in O.R.

01:32:20.636 --> 01:32:22.605
[monitor beeping]

01:32:28.944 --> 01:32:30.613
[Taps on glass]

01:32:32.347 --> 01:32:35.217
Miss, I'm sorry,
but y'all need
to leave now.

01:32:35.250 --> 01:32:37.686
No, we're not
going anywhere.

01:32:37.720 --> 01:32:39.221
I'm sorry.
It's the rules.

01:32:39.254 --> 01:32:41.123
Well, you know,
you can...

01:32:41.156 --> 01:32:42.991
You know what you
can do with your rules.

01:32:43.025 --> 01:32:44.059
Ma'am, please.

01:32:44.092 --> 01:32:46.028
