how serious the
situation is here?

01:32:59.141 --> 01:33:02.144
Yeah. I think
we all do.

01:33:02.177 --> 01:33:04.246
Hi, folks.
Are you his wife?

01:33:04.279 --> 01:33:06.381
Girlfriend.

01:33:06.414 --> 01:33:07.382
Hi.
Hi.

01:33:07.415 --> 01:33:08.383
Sunny Thompson.
Dr. Enzler.

01:33:08.416 --> 01:33:10.218
I'm Dr. Enzler.

01:33:10.252 --> 01:33:11.787
Sunny,
as you know,

01:33:11.820 --> 01:33:13.989
he's had
a very serious
brain injury.

01:33:14.022 --> 01:33:16.825
Now, we've done
a procedure to relieve
some of the pressure,

01:33:16.859 --> 01:33:18.727
but when
the brain's injured,
it swells,

01:33:18.761 --> 01:33:20.696
