additional damage.

01:33:20.729 --> 01:33:24.032
How much,
we don't know yet.

01:33:24.066 --> 01:33:25.968
We tried
to stabilize him,

01:33:26.001 --> 01:33:28.704
but the next 12 hours
are gonna be critical.

01:33:28.737 --> 01:33:30.873
Meaning?

01:33:30.906 --> 01:33:34.109
Meaning we're
doing everything
we can for him.

01:33:34.142 --> 01:33:35.778
I think it's all right
if they stay.

01:33:42.350 --> 01:33:44.687
