01:33:46.288 --> 01:33:48.223
you need anything,

01:33:48.256 --> 01:33:49.391
anything at all,

01:33:49.424 --> 01:33:51.727
we are
right outside, okay?

01:33:53.261 --> 01:33:55.698
I need him.

01:34:01.336 --> 01:34:05.040
Put more cream
in the ice cream
and less salt, then...

01:34:07.009 --> 01:34:09.244
[sighs]

01:34:09.277 --> 01:34:11.079
Hey.

01:34:11.113 --> 01:34:12.781
Is he gonna
be okay?

01:34:15.317 --> 01:34:18.086
What's the ballpark
for how long
he's gonna be...

01:34:18.120 --> 01:34:19.187
What did they say?

01:34:19.221 --> 01:34:20.756
Is there
any word from...

01:34:24.793 --> 01:34:26.394
[sighs]

01:34:38.440 --> 01:34:39.975
[Sighs]

01:35:07.936 --> 01:35:10.205
[Siren blaring]

01:35:10.238 --> 01:35:12.174
[Monitor beeping]

01:35:23.919 --> 01:35:25.821
Come on, Butch.

01:35:26.955 --> 01:35:28.924
Answer me.

01:35:30.225 --> 01:35:33.328
This is no way
to start a relationship.

01:35:35.097 --> 01:35:38.033
I still got so much
to learn from you.

01:35:41.536 --> 01:35:43.505
Answer me, Butch!

01:35:45.173 --> 01:35:46.374
Come on!

01:35:46.408 --> 01:35:49.344
I know you been through
harder than this!

01:35:49.377 --> 01:35:51.046
Fight, damn it!

01:35:51.079 --> 01:35:52.981
You said you
wouldn't leave me!

01:35:53.015 --> 01:35:54.249
You promised!

01:35:54.282 --> 01:35:56.451
You promised.

01:35:56.484 --> 01:35:58.420
[Crying]

01:36:08.263 --> 01:36:10.198
[Alarm beeping softly]

01:36:43.899 --> 01:36:44.867
[Beeping fades]

01:37:17.365 --> 01:37:19.034
Cotton.

01:37:26.241 --> 01:37:28.343
It's time
to say goodbye.

01:37:36.451 --> 01:37:39.187
Looks like he went
real peacefully.

01:37:39.221 --> 01:37:41.423
He did everything
he wanted to do.

01:37:46.294 --> 01:37:48.096
No! No, no, no!
No, no, no, no!

01:37:48.130 --> 01:37:50.065
He's not dead!

01:37:50.098 --> 01:37:51.599
