off of him!

01:37:51.633 --> 01:37:52.600
He's not dead!

01:37:52.634 --> 01:37:54.036
He's not dead.

01:37:54.069 --> 01:37:55.337
Butch.

01:37:55.370 --> 01:37:57.105
Butch, can't you
hear me? Please!

01:37:57.139 --> 01:37:59.274
He's not dead, okay?
He's fine.

