Please, Butch,
listen to me!

01:38:03.511 --> 01:38:05.447
Listen to me!

01:38:05.480 --> 01:38:08.450
He's just having
a bad dream!

01:38:08.483 --> 01:38:10.052
Sunny, you have
to wake him up!

01:38:10.085 --> 01:38:12.087
Honey,
I can't wake him up.

01:38:12.120 --> 01:38:13.155
[Sobbing]

01:38:14.489 --> 01:38:16.424
I know, honey.

01:38:25.300 --> 01:38:26.268
Hey...

01:38:28.236 --> 01:38:29.504
I know.

01:38:34.309 --> 01:38:36.211
Okay.

01:38:36.244 --> 01:38:38.646
Come here, baby.

01:38:38.680 --> 01:38:40.182
No.

01:38:40.215 --> 01:38:42.150
[Siren blaring outside]

01:38:51.559 --> 01:38:54.429
He's my best friend.

01:38:54.462 --> 01:38:56.999
I know.

