* Are there angels
in the wilderness? *

01:39:00.435 --> 01:39:03.238
* I don't know

01:39:06.674 --> 01:39:10.078
* I've got my doubts

01:39:10.112 --> 01:39:13.015
* But if you say so

01:39:16.251 --> 01:39:19.187
* But I got a feeling

01:39:19.221 --> 01:39:22.624
* That we're doing okay

01:39:24.692 --> 01:39:26.294
