* When you ask for bread

01:39:40.808 --> 01:39:42.177
* Will I give you stone...

01:39:42.210 --> 01:39:44.046
I heard about Butch.

01:39:44.046 --> 01:39:45.447
He was
too young to...

01:39:45.480 --> 01:39:46.514
Hey, save it.

