01:41:58.713 --> 01:42:00.248
Cotton,
put the gun down.

01:42:00.282 --> 01:42:01.783
He did it!
I know, honey. Please.

01:42:01.816 --> 01:42:03.518
Please put the gun down
for me. Please.

01:42:03.551 --> 01:42:04.886
He didn't... He didn't know
