01:42:04.919 --> 01:42:06.221
He's just a horse.

01:42:06.254 --> 01:42:09.324
I want him back.

01:42:09.357 --> 01:42:11.759
I want him back now!

01:42:11.793 --> 01:42:14.896
I know. I know.
I want him back, too,
but we've got...

01:42:14.929 --> 01:42:16.598
Cotton,
I want him back, too.

01:42:16.631 --> 01:42:18.200
This is not
gonna get him back.

01:42:18.200 --> 01:42:21.436
I miss the way
he would look at me,

01:42:21.469 --> 01:42:23.438
the way
he would stay there

01:42:23.471 --> 01:42:25.673
