to sleep at night

01:42:25.707 --> 01:42:27.475
'cause he knew
I was scared.

01:42:28.610 --> 01:42:30.212
I miss that!

01:42:30.245 --> 01:42:31.213
I know.

01:42:31.246 --> 01:42:32.514
I loved him, too.

01:42:32.547 --> 01:42:34.282
We both loved him.

01:42:34.316 --> 01:42:35.817
That's what he gave us.

01:42:35.850 --> 01:42:38.453
