01:43:27.702 --> 01:43:28.870
Sunny.

01:43:28.903 --> 01:43:30.572
Oh, hey.

01:43:30.605 --> 01:43:31.973
I'm sorry to bother you.

01:43:32.006 --> 01:43:33.941
Maybe... Maybe I should
come back later.

01:43:33.975 --> 01:43:35.943
Oh, no, you're
not bothering me.

01:43:35.977 --> 01:43:37.545
What's up?

01:43:37.579 --> 01:43:39.647
