if Butch told you,

01:43:39.681 --> 01:43:42.016
but he set it up for y'all
to play on the radio.

01:43:42.049 --> 01:43:44.819
What are you
talking about?

01:43:44.852 --> 01:43:46.954
He went to Cheryl.
She was at the hospital,

01:43:46.988 --> 01:43:49.491
