he made a deal for you.

01:43:56.464 --> 01:43:58.633
You're gonna
lose Jack-O-Lopes,
aren't you?

01:44:00.067 --> 01:44:02.304
Don't matter.

01:44:02.337 --> 01:44:05.773
I am tired of standing
behind three feet of Formica,

01:44:05.807 --> 01:44:08.610
