about how it were.

01:44:08.643 --> 01:44:10.478
[Chuckles]

01:44:10.512 --> 01:44:13.315
Time to cut
and live, Sunny.

01:44:14.616 --> 01:44:16.384
Good for you.

01:44:18.019 --> 01:44:20.755
